            <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tr>
        <td>Minefields</td>
        <td>30</td>
        <td>Allows deployment of 5 AD5 mines in the Advance Deployment Zone -before- deploying squadrons.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
