        <td>30</td>
        <td>Allows re-rolls of ONE die for determining strategic/operational advantage in this and adjacent territories. Example: You roll 3 and 1 for advantage. You may re-roll the 1, resulting in a 4 and a resulting advantage roll of 7. See Operational Assets v1.3 page 5 for statistics.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
