        <td>30 + (0-50)</td>
        <td>You may deploy up to 80 points of Tower Defensive Line. Each additional 10 RP spent is +40 points, up to a maximum of 50 additional RP for a maximum points value of 280. Mark the towers on the Operational Theatre Map as well as their weapon options. See the entry for Tower Defensive Line in each player's respective army list for statistics.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Bunker Complex</td>
        <td>50</td>
        <td>Mark the bunker on the Operational Theatre Map. See the entry for Bunker Complex in each player's respective army list for statistics.</td>
    </tr>
</table>

