<h2 id="Alliances">Alliances</h2>
<p>
    Players start out as part of one of three governing alliances: the Grand Coalition, the Imperial Bond and the Free Nations. Default allegiances are used, e.g. Prussian players start in the Imperial Bond and FSA players start in the Grand Coalition. Default alliance rules as detailed in the rulebook are in effect, with the following adjustments.
    Players may only include allied detachments that consist of nations that are not actively participating in the campaign (e.g. the French Republic can take allies from the Ottoman Empire). If a player wishes to include detachments from a nation that is active in this campaign, both players must be part of the same alliance. Furthermore, permission to use the allied detachment must be granted by the allied nation.
</p>
